EmailTemplate.name: Toronto Sportsmen's Show Invitation
EmailTemplate.subject: Come on out to the Toronto Sportsmen's Show!
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hey {!Contact.FirstName},
I hope that you're as excited for Spring as we are! We've had a very good Show Season so far and we're hoping to keep that momentum going with the Toronto Sportsmen's Show!
If you're familiar with the Sportsmen's Show, you'll notice that it is back to it's original time and location! The last couple of years, it's been earlier in the season and some folks have missed it entirely. Now that it's back in it's rightful place there will be more exhibits, booths, people and most importantly of all, more boats!
Please feel free to give me a call, text or email to book your time to see Legend Boats at the Toronto Sportsmen's Show, happening March 16-20 at The International Centre.
Legend is guaranteed to have the best booth in the Show and we're also carrying our amazing Boat Show Season deals over to our final show of the season and you just can't pass them up.
Legend is rewarding you for buying early during their Boat Show Me the Money Event.
Here are just a few of the benefits of investing in a summer full of memories now:
Save up to $2000 off engine upgrades Save up to $1000 off Pontoon Enclosures No Interest, No Payments until Summer Guaranteed delivery date
Pick up times are even still available for the Spring, but they're going fast!
Thanks again for your time and I'll talk to you soon
Yours in Boating,
{!User.Name} {!User.Title}
{!User.Phone} {!User.Email} legendboats.com
